                <div class="testimonial-card h-100">
                    <div class="testimonial-text">
                        "From the mehndi to the vidaai, every moment was captured beautifully. They made us feel so comfortable throughout!"
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">
                        <img src="/images/client3.jpg" alt="Neha & Amit" class="testimonial-avatar">
                        <div>
                            <strong>Neha & Amit</strong>
                            <div class="text-muted">Gujarati Wedding, Ahmedabad</div>
                        </div>
